  [Text] Iran's foreign minister, Mr. Velayati, has invited 
his Pakistani counterpart to take part in the ministerial 
meeting of the Economic Cooperation Organization [ECO] to be 
held in Tehran from 25 to 26 January. 
  The invitation was handed over by the Iranian Foreign 
