  [Excerpt] To the righteous soul will be said: O thou soul, 
in complete rest and satisfaction, come back thou to thy lord, 
well pleased thyself, and well-pleasing unto him. Enter thou, 
then, among my devotees. Yea, enter thou my heaven. [koranic 
