<F P=102>  NC0701085694 Beirut AL-SHIRA' in Arabic 3 Jan 94 p 7 </F>
<F P=103> NC0701085694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut AL-SHIRA' </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yasir 'Arafat has an interest in delaying the 
Israeli withdrawal from Gaza and Jericho: His security agencies 
are not yet complete. After establishing the armed force 
(police and public security), 'Arafat now wants to create 
security services for the presidency and national security 
(intelligence) to control any security problem from the 
opposition Palestinian forces. 
  Arab sources told AL-SHIRA' that 'Arafat is deliberately 
procrastinating at the negotiations, setting conditions that are 
not mentioned in the Gaza-Jericho agreement he signed with 
Israel. He is buying time to prepare his own security. 

