  [Text] Cairo, 9 Jan (MENA)--President Husni Mubarak has 
received a report from Minister of Interior Hasan al-Alfi on the 
proceedings of the Arab interior ministers' meetings held in 
Tunis recently. 
  After a meeting with President Mubarak today, al-Alfi said 
the main topic of discussion at the conference was security 
cooperation to prevent crime and combat narcotics, forgery, and 
