<F P=102>  TA0701194794 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1830 GMT 7 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0701194794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
