<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Professor Itamar Rabinovich, Israel's ambassador to 
the United States and head of the Israeli team for negotiations 
with Syria, will come to Israel next week for consultations over 
the meeting between Presidents Clinton and al-Asad. Our 
political correspondent Gadi Sukenik reports that, after the 
meeting, Ambassador Rabinovich will hold a series of tete-a-tete 
