<H3> <TI>   IDF Reacts to Betzelem Report </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0901202794 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1800 GMT 9 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0901202794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] has commented on 
the Betzelem report about Arabs cooperating with the authorities 
in the territories. It says this is the first time that 
Betzelem has focused on the activities of Arab terrorist 
organizations vis-a-vis the internal Arab population. During 
the intifadah, the IDF says, most of the 964 Palestinians 
murdered by other Palestinians did not cooperate in any way with 
the IDF. The Army stressed its obligation to do everything 
required to support those individuals who have aided the Israeli 
authorities over the years. 

</TEXT>

