  [Text] A U.S. Congressional delegation gathering 
information on Israeli soldiers who went missing in Lebanon 12 
years ago arrived in al-Biqa' today. Senior Lebanese Army 
intelligence officers and a high-ranking U.S. diplomat received 
the delegation at al-Masna' on the Lebanese-Syrian border. 
  The delegation began its mission with a visit to 'Ayta 
al-Fakhkhar, where it met the mayor and the parish priest. The 
