<H3> <TI>   Visiting Russian Envoy on Karabakh Crisis </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0801205694 Tehran IRNA in English 2022 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0801205694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRNA </F>


